required_parameters.name: style
required_parameters.description:
Available style are

```
ACG
Cyberpunk
Realistic
Watercolor
Synthwave
Game CG
Tarot
Ink and Wask
Chibi
Asian
Pastel Colors
```

required_parameters.name: prompt
required_parameters.description: Describe your fantasy in parameter prompt. More detail your prompt more great the image result.
required_parameters.default: portrait of a beautiful girl, gal, gyaru, (blush:1.3, blush stickers), sketch, shy, illustration, beautiful, red eyes, messy blond hair, oversize sweater over shirt, bow tie, standing, knee shot, eye-level shot, (pure background|simple background), style of manga, taking a selfie from mirror

required_parameters.name: controlNet
required_parameters.description:
along with parameter `init_image`

Available controlNet

```
openpose
scribble
hed
canny
```

Default `none`

required_parameters.name: sampler
required_parameters.description:
Available sampler are

```
Euler a
Euler
LMS
Heun
DPM2
DPM2 a
DPM++ 2S a
DPM++ 2M
DPM++ SDE
DPM fast
DPM adaptive
LMS Karras
DPM2 Karras
DPM2 a Karras
DPM++ 2S a Karras
DPM++ 2M Karras
DPM++ SDE Karras
DDIM
```

optional_parameters.name: negative_prompt
optional_parameters.description: describe anything that you don't want appear in image
optional_parameters.default: ((NSFW)), naked, nude, no clothes, upper body uncovered, breast uncovered, (worst quality, low quality, extra digits:1.4),artist name, nsfw, monochrome, fused face, poorly drawn face, cloned face, false body, false face, bad hands, poorly drawn hands, fused eyes, poorly drawn eyes, liquid eyes, false eyes, scary, ugly
